      "description": "## What's New\r\n\r\nAddressed [feedbacks](https://github.com/obsidianmd/obsidian-releases/pull/8099#issuecomment-4230247399):\r\n\r\n- Better flexibility over how dates and times are parsed within the plugin settings.\r\n- Task styling has been completely offloaded to CSS.\r\n- The plugin now imports Obsidian's built-in `moment`.\r\n- The plugin now uses HTML `data-*` attributes for date categories.\r\n- Prefixed CSS classes and variables to prevent conflict with other Obsidian themes and plugins.",
